custom.schema_definition:
mistvalidator.AllowedWhenValueIsIn(
  path.MatchRelative().AtParent().AtName("type"),
  []attr.Value{
    types.StringValue("eap"),
    types.StringValue("eap192"),
    types.StringValue("psk"),
    types.StringValue("psk-tkip"),
    types.StringValue("psk-wpa2-tkip"),
  },
)

string.description:
information to set in the `circuit_id` field of the DHCP Option 82. It is possible to use static string or the following variables (e.g. `{{SSID}}:{{AP_MAC}}`):
  * {{AP_MAC}}
  * {{AP_MAC_DASHED}}
  * {{AP_MODEL}}
  * {{AP_NAME}}
  * {{SITE_NAME}}
  * {{SSID}}

